Looked at a huge variety of
great visualizations, and

134
00:08:32.958 --> 00:08:38.390
then we've pulled it all together with
a stunning interactive dashboard.

135
00:08:38.390 --> 00:08:40.715
That's all we have to show you for
now, but

136
00:08:40.715 --> 00:08:43.437
we look forward to seeing
what you have to show us.

